Will you be taking part in One Big Fancy Dress Friday? Here are some selfie tips form Alessandra Marshall One Big Fancy Dress Friday Halloselfie tips - Daily Record If you're taking part in One Big Fancy Dress Friday, we'd love you to share your selfies with us.
 You can email them to sundaymail100@sundaymail.co.uk, tweet them using #halloselfie to @sundaymail100 or post them to our Facebook Page . 
Our charity volunteer Alessandra Marshall from Mearns Castle High School in Glasgow shared her tips for taking a good selfie. We think she looks great in her accessories, don't you?
